      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To The Living Section:</p>
        <p>Your article "Elegant (and Loathing) Memories of Childhood and Junket"  [ Jan. 2 ]  captured the original taste. What about a follow-up on Danish Dessert, that suave, violet-hued delight of the 1950's, now seemingly gone the way of the LP record? Many would savor such a piece. HOWARD SAGE New York, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
